entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwen pa renmen isit la." t="I don't like this place." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Manman mwen kontan sitiyasyon an pap dire." t="Thank goodness this is all temporary." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Yon lòt envayisè… Rale kò nou!" t="Another intruder… Fall back!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ey, Ey,Ey soti sou teritwa mwen." t="Eh, eh, eh. Get off my turf." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Non fout." t="Oh hell no." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Lage zam ou." t="Drop your weapon." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Sispann voye kaka." t="Stop that shit." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Tout bon vre? Ou koumanse yon bagay?" t="For real? You startin' somethin'?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mèsi." t="Thank you." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Poki tout bri sa yo?" t="So why all the fuss?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Oh-ho." t="Oh-ho." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Alo? Pa gen moun la?" t="Hello? Anyone there?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="'Se pa anyen." t="It's nothing." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Kalma. Pa gen pèsonn la a." t="No point. There's no one here." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Eyh… Pouki sa pou fè sa pran bann tan sa a?" t="Ehh… why draw this out?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Pa fè enbesil. Soti kote ou ye a." t="Don't be a jerk. Come out." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Yon nan moun pa nou yo atè." t="One of ours is down." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwen konprann patron." t="Understood." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Nou fout pran nan pèlen!!" t="'S a fuckin' ambush!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Bò isit! Fanm lan ap atake m!" t="Over here! She's attacking me!" b="" a=""/>

entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Kenbe menm fòmasyon an! Nou se yon ekip!" t="Stay in formation! We're a team!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Bò isit! Vini jwenn mwen! " t="To me! Rally to me!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Regwoupe!" t="Regroup!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Fè atansyon." t="Watch it." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Gade kote w prale, madanm." t="Watch where you're goin', lady." b="" a=""/>
entries.maleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Gade kote w prale, madanm', man." t="Watch where you're goin', man." b="" a=""/>

entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Alo" t="Hello." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Yo… Fèmen dan w epi verifye si bagay la ploge… priz la sou men gòch ou…" t="Yo…shut your mouth…and check if it's plugged in…socket's on the left." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Byen sa ou wè devan ou??" t="Um… Well… What's it say on the display…?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwen sou lèl la!" t="I'm on the flanks!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="An nou pase pa sou kote!" t="Taking the flank!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Desann tèt ou!" t="Get down!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Wi, okipe tèt ou." t="Yeah, take care yourself." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwen pa konprann anyen..." t="I don’t get it…" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="An nou fè vit." t="Get a move on." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Fòk nou veyatif anpil. Se pou tout bon." t="High alert. I mean it." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Pa annik kanpe la a." t="Don't just stand there staring." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Pa rete, kontinye goumen! Jis ke nan lanmò a!" t="Don't stop, keep fighting! To the death!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ahkh…. Khhh.... Non... pitye... Non... Mwen pa vle..." t="Khhh…. Khhh.... No... Mercy... No... Don't… want…" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ok se sa, eseye sou bò gòch ou… Epi…? Mwen fout di w." t="Ok great, then try on the left… And…? I fuckin' told you." b="" a=""/>

<kiroshi l="creo" o="Risèt sistem la …Wi… Wi, map tann… Mm… Se sa, mwen gen tout tan mwen… Epi...? Bon, pran plezi w." t="System reset…Yeah… Yes, I'm waiting… Mm… Yeah I got time… So...? Great, have fun." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Na tounen sou sa yon lòt lè." t="We'll pick this up some other time." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="An nou tounen sou sa nou tap pale an." t="Let's get back to the issue at hand." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Fè pi vit!" t="Faster!" b="" a=""/>
